---
---
<section class="bg-bg-bone py-20 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-fg leading-tight">
          Temukan Buku <span class="text-primary">Favoritmu</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-fg-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Jelajahi ribuan koleksi buku dari berbagai genre. Dari fiksi hingga non-fiksi, 
          kami punya semua yang kamu butuhkan untuk menambah wawasan.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4">
          <a href="/books" class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-fg font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-md transition-colors">
            Jelajahi Katalog
          </a>
          <a href="#categories" class="border border-border hover:border-primary text-fg font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-md transition-colors">
            Lihat Kategori
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative h-96 hidden md:block">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-8 w-36 h-52 rounded-lg shadow-level2 overflow-hidden transform rotate-[-6deg] hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300">
          <img src="https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/isbn/9789793062792-L.jpg" alt="Laskar Pelangi" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute top-8 left-36 w-36 h-52 rounded-lg shadow-level2 overflow-hidden transform rotate-[4deg] hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300 z-10">
          <img src="https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/isbn/9780735211292-L.jpg" alt="Atomic Habits" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute top-16 right-8 w-36 h-52 rounded-lg shadow-level2 overflow-hidden transform rotate-[8deg] hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300 z-20">
          <img src="https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/isbn/9780590353427-L.jpg" alt="Harry Potter" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-20 w-36 h-52 rounded-lg shadow-level2 overflow-hidden transform rotate-[-3deg] hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300 z-30">
          <img src="https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/isbn/9780062316097-L.jpg" alt="Sapiens" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
